 <category domain="http://news.thaipbs.or.th/category/tags/%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%99%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%B3%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%88%E0%B8%8A%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%A2%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%B7%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%A7%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B0%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%A0%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%95%E0%B8%B4">ปันน้ำใจช่วยเหลือสัตว์ประสบภัยพิบัติ</category>
